cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.SD

The paper proposes a new algorithm for multitask clustering, which involves learning a shared feature representation and task relationships. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm also involves clustering text data (cs.CL) and image data (cs.CV), which are common applications of clustering. Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques (cs.SD) to solve the proposed objectives.
